 <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
 <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
 
 <h3>Service Provision</h3>
 <ul>
 <li>To provide and maintain our website and services</li>
 <li>To process and respond to your inquiries</li>
 <li>To send you updates about our launch and new features</li>
 <li>To curate and recommend relevant content</li>
 </ul>

 <h3>Communication</h3>
 <ul>
 <li>To send you newsletters and marketing communications (with your consent)</li>
 <li>To respond to your questions and provide customer support</li>
 <li>To notify you about changes to our services or policies</li>
 </ul>

 <h3>Improvement and Analytics</h3>
 <ul>
 <li>To analyze website usage and improve our services</li>
 <li>To understand user preferences and behavior</li>
 <li>To develop new features and functionality</li>
 <li>To monitor and ensure the security of our services</li>
 </ul>

 <h3>Legal and Compliance</h3>
 <ul>
 <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
 <li>To protect our rights and prevent fraud</li>
 <li>To enforce our terms of service</li>
 </ul>
 </section>

